'''大卫·马汉'''（David N. Magang，出生于1938年）是一位[[博茨瓦纳|博茨瓦纳]]律师、商人和政治人物。他毕业于伦敦大学，是博茨瓦纳开办私人法律实践的首个本地人。<ref>[http://www.phakalane.com/news/2009/aug/05/launch-of-the-magic-of-perserverance/ Biography:Launch of The Magic of Perserverance] {{Wayback|url=http://www.phakalane.com/news/2009/aug/05/launch-of-the-magic-of-perserverance/ |date=20190911011345 }}. Phakalane ltd. website.  Retrieved 2010-02-12.</ref> 马汉是[[博茨瓦纳民主党|博茨瓦纳民主党]]党员，1979年至2002年任Kweneng East/Lentsweletau选区议会部长。在[[奎特·马西雷|奎特·马西雷]]、[[费斯图斯·莫加埃|费斯图斯·莫加埃]]总统任期内，他担任一系列部长职位，包括矿产资源和水务部部长(1994-97)、工程交通及通讯部部长(1992-94, 1998-2001)。1989年至1992年马汉还担任[[非洲开发银行|非洲开发银行]]总裁。离开政务后马汉又投身商界。<ref>[http://allafrica.com/stories/200904150731.html Botswana: Magang Transforms Virgin Land Into a Paradise] {{Wayback|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/200904150731.html |date=20121013120857 }}. Mmegi/The Reporter (Gaborone), Lekopanye Mooketsi. 15 April 2009.</ref> 2002年出版了自传。<ref>[http://www.sundaystandard.info/search/search_item.php?NewsID=4216 A Review of David Magang’s “MAGIC OF PERSEVERANCE”]. Christian John Makgala, Sunday Standard. 18 January 2009.</ref><ref>[http://www.sarwatch.org/headline-news-for-botwana/177-mining-and-politics-in-botwana/1075-did-de-beers-cheat-botswana--the-masire-factor.html   Did De Beers cheat Botswana? – The Masire Factor] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sarwatch.org/headline-news-for-botwana/177-mining-and-politics-in-botwana/1075-did-de-beers-cheat-botswana--the-masire-factor.html |date=20100411064638 }}. Sunday Standard. 18 January 2010.</ref><ref>[http://allafrica.com/stories/200807140846.html Botswana: Magang's 'Unputdownable' Memoirs] {{Wayback|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/200807140846.html |date=20121013120933 }}. Mmegi/The Reporter (Gaborone). 11 July 2008</ref>

